quran[53]{c,v,t}:
  51,31,"Iye adati, “Kodi inu Atumwi uthenga wanu ndi wotani?”"
  51,32,"Iwo adati, “Ife tatumidwa kwa anthu ochimwa.”"
  51,33,“Kuti tigwetse pa iwo miyala yamakande.”
  51,34,“Idakonzedwa ndi Ambuye wako kudza kwa anthu oswa malamulo.”
  51,35,Ndipo Ife tidatulutsa anthu okhulupirira amene adali momwemo
  51,36,Koma sitidapezemo mabanja a Chisilamu kupatula banja limodzi lokha basi
  51,37,Ndipo Ife tidasiyamo chizindikiro kwa iwo amene amaopa chilango chowawa
  51,38,Ndi mwa Mose. Pamene tidamutumiza kwa Farawo ndi zizindikiro zooneka
  51,39,"Koma Farawo adakana pamodzi ndi mafumu ake nati, “Ndiwe munthu wamatsenga kapena munthu wa misala.”"
  51,40,Motero tidamugwira pamodzi ndi gulu la asirikali ake ndi kuwamiza onse m’nyanja pamene iye ndiye adali wolakwa
  51,41,Ndipo mwa a Aad pamene tidawatumizira mphepo yoononga
  51,42,Imene sidasiye chilichonse chimene idalimbana nacho kupatula kuchiononga ndi kuchisandutsa phulusa
  51,43,"Ndipo mwa anthu a Thamoud. Pamene adauzidwa kuti, “Basangalalani kanthawi kochepa.”"
  51,44,"Koma iwo adaphwanya lamulo la Ambuye wawo mwamwano, kotero mabingu adawaononga iwo ali kuona"
  51,45,Kotero iwo adalibe mphamvu zodzuka kapena zodzitetezera
  51,46,Ndi anthu a Nowa iwo asanadze. Ndithudi iwo adali anthu oswa malamulo
  51,47,"Ife tidakonza kumwamba mwamphamvu ndiponso mwaluso. Ndipo, ndithudi, ndife amene timapanga kukula kwa mlengalenga"
  51,48,"Ndipo dziko, tidamwaza. Kodi ndife omwaza bwino bwanji"
  51,49,Ndipo zonse zimene tidalenga tidazilenga ziwiriziwiri kuti mukhoza kukumbukira
  51,50,Kotero thawirani kwa Mulungu. Ndithudi Ine ndine mchenjezi wooneka kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,51,Ndipo musapange fano kukhala lopembedzedwa pamodzi ndi Mulungu. Ndithudi ine ndine mchenjezi wooneka kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,52,"Chimodzimodzi palibe Mtumwi amene adadza kwa anthu amene sadamunenere mawu ofanana monga akuti: “Wamatsenga kapena munthu wopenga!”"
  51,53,"Kodi uwu ndi mwambo umene akhala ali kusiyirana wina ndi mnzake? Iyayi, iwo ndi anthu amene ali kuswa malamulo mopyola muyeso"
  51,54,Kotero uwaleke chifukwa iwe ulibe mlandu
  51,55,Ndipo kumbutsa chifukwa chikumbutso chimathandiza anthu okhulupirira
  51,56,Ndipo Ine ndidalenga majini ndi anthu kuti azindipembedza Ine
  51,57,Ine sindiwapempha chakudya ndipo sindiwafunsa kuti azindidyetsa Ine
  51,58,"Ndithudi ndi Mulungu yekha amene amapereka chakudya chonse, Mwini mphamvu zonse ndi wolimba kwambiri"
  51,59,"Ndithudi anthu onse olakwa adzalandira gawo longa limene anzawo olakwa akale adalandira, kotero asandifunse Ine kuchita mofulumira"
  51,60,Kotero tsoka kwa onse osakhulupirira kuchokera ku tsiku lomwe iwo alonjezedwa
  52,1,Ndi pali phiri
  52,2,Ndi pali Buku lolemekezeka
  52,3,Lili chikopa chosapinda
  52,4,Ndi pali Bait – Ul-Ma’mur (Nyumba imene ili kumwamba yolingana ndi Kaaba imene ili ku Makka ndipo imaonedwa ndi angelo pafupipafupi)
  52,5,Ndi pali denga lonyamuka
  52,6,Ndi pali nyanja yodzadzidwa ndi madzi ambiri
  52,7,Ndithudi chilango cha Ambuye wako chidzakwaniritsidwa
  52,8,Palibe wina amene angachiletse
  52,9,"Pa tsiku limeneli, kumwamba kudzagwedezeka koopsa"
  52,10,Ndipo mapiri adzagudubuzika osakhalanso china chake
  52,11,"Kotero tsoka, patsiku limeneli kwa anthu abodza"
  52,12,Amene amatangwanika ndi mabodza
  52,13,Patsikuli iwo adzatengedwa ndi kuponyedwa mwamphamvu ku moto wa ku Gahena
  52,14,Uwu ndi moto umene mumati ndi bodza
  52,15,Kodi amenewa ndi matsenga kapena simutha kuona
  52,16,"Lawani kutentha kwake ndipo kaya inu mupirira kapena ayi, kwa inu ndi chimodzimodzi; inu muli kulandira malipiro a ntchito zomwe mumachita"
  52,17,"Ndithudi iwo amene ali olungama, adzakhala m’minda mwamtendere"
  52,18,Kusangalala chifukwa cha zimene Ambuye wawo wawapatsa ndipo Ambuye wawo wawapulumutsa ku chilango cha ku Gahena
  52,19,“Idyani ndi kumwa mwachisangalalo chifukwa cha ntchito zanu zabwino zomwe mudachita.”
  52,20,"Iwo adzakhala pa mipando yawofowofo, yoikidwa m’mizere. Ndipo Ife tidzawakwatitsa kwa amene ali ndi maso akuluakulu ndi okongola"
  52,21,"Ndipo iwo amene amakhulupirira ndipo ana awo amawatsatira m’chipembedzo, oterewa tidzawakumaniza ndi mabanja awo ndipo Ife sitidzawachotsera chilichonse cha malipiro a ntchito zawo zabwino. Munthu aliyense adzafunsidwa malinga ndi ntchito zake"
  52,22,Ndipo tidzawapatsa zipatso ndi nyama zimene iwo afuna
  52,23,Kumeneko iwo adzapatsana wina ndi mnzake chikho chimene mulibe zinthu zopanda pake kapena uchimo